{"name": "fireflies-cli", "metadata": {"name": "fireflies-cli", "version": "0.1.0", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "https://github.com/trilogy-group/pocs", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["click", "python-dotenv", "fireflies-sdk"], "summary": "Command line interface for Fireflies.ai", "upload_time": 1734634517}, "documentation": ["# Fireflies CLI\n\nCommand line interface for Fireflies.ai. This package provides a convenient way to interact with Fireflies.ai from the command line.\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\npip install fireflies-cli\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```bash\n# Set your API key (only needed once)\nff config set-key YOUR_API_KEY\n\n# Join a meeting\nff join --url https://meet.google.com/xxx-yyyy-zzz\n\n# Get video URL for a transcript\nff video TRANSCRIPT_ID\n\n# Download video\nff video -d TRANSCRIPT_ID\n\n# List recent transcripts\nff list\n\n# Delete a transcript\nff delete TRANSCRIPT_ID\n```\n\n## Features\n\n- Join meetings with optional duration and name\n- Get video URLs for transcripts\n- Download meeting recordings\n- List transcripts\n- Delete transcripts\n\n## Note\n\nThis CLI tool uses the `fireflies-sdk` package. If you need programmatic access to Fireflies.ai, consider using the SDK directly.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "fireflies_cli", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "fireflies_cli.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "fireflies_cli.cli", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "fireflies_cli.cli.get_api", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Get FirefliesAPI instance using API key from environment"]}, {"name": "fireflies_cli.cli.cli", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Fireflies.ai CLI"]}, {"name": "fireflies_cli.cli.config", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Configure the CLI"]}, {"name": "fireflies_cli.cli.set_api_key", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "api_key", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Set your Fireflies API key"]}, {"name": "fireflies_cli.cli.key", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "api_key", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Set your Fireflies API key"]}, {"name": "fireflies_cli.cli.join", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "duration", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "name", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "url", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Join a meeting"]}, {"name": "fireflies_cli.cli.video", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "identifier", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "download", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Get video URL for a transcript (use transcript ID)"]}, {"name": "fireflies_cli.cli.download", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "transcript_id", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "output", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Download video for a transcript"]}, {"name": "fireflies_cli.cli.list", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "limit", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["List recent transcripts"]}, {"name": "fireflies_cli.cli.transcript", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "transcript_id", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Get full transcript text"]}, {"name": "fireflies_cli.cli.participants", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "transcript_id", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Get meeting participants"]}, {"name": "fireflies_cli.cli.delete", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "transcript_id", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documenta